ive.org/web/20180915085526/http://www.laliga.es/en/news/the-201415-liga-bbva-ideal-xi |archive-date=15 September 2018 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n* [[FIFA World Cup awards#All-Star Team|FIFA World Cup Dream Team]]: [[2014 FIFA World Cup#Dream Team|2014]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Dream Team Winners Earn Sony Prizes |publisher=FIFA |date=23 July 2014 |url=https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=7/news=dream-team-winners-earn-sony-prizes-2406063.html |accessdate=27 August 2015}}</ref>\n* [[Copa Am\u00e9rica records and statistics|Copa Am\u00e9rica Dream Team]]: [[2007 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2007]], [[2011 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2011]], [[2015 Copa Am\u00e9rica#Team of the tournament|2015]], [[Copa Am\u00e9rica Centenario|2016]]<ref>{{cite news |title=El Once Ideal de la Copa Am\u00e9rica |trans-title=The Ideal Eleven of the Copa Am\u00e9rica |newspaper=La Rep\u00fablica |language=Spanish |date=16 July 2007 |url=http://larepublica.pe/16-07-2007/el-once-ideal-de-la-copa-america |accessdate=16 February 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229220113/http://larepublica.pe/16-07-2007/el-once-ideal-de-la-copa-america |archive-date=29 December 2016 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"The Copa Am\u00e9rica 2011 Dream Team\">{{cite web |title=The Copa Am\u00e9rica 2011 Dream Team |publisher=Copa America Organisation |date=8 June 2015 |url=http://www.ca2015.com/en/gallery/the-copa-america-2011-dream-team/t8bquapogxrw10j9h0aa6h9d7/slide/8 |accessdate=13 September 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150930010155/http://www.ca2015.com/en/gallery/the-copa-america-2011-dream-team/t8bquapogxrw10j9h0aa6h9d7/slide/8 |archivedate=30 September 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Copa Am\u00e9rica 2015: Team of the Tournament |publisher=Copa America Organisation |date=5 July 2015 |url=http://www.ca2015.com/en/gallery/copa-america-2015---team-of-the-tournament/1nqqmzngdosa911z9l2g8k8317/slide/9 |accessdate=27 August 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150902002042/http://www.ca2015.com/en/gallery/copa-america-2015---team-of-the-tournament/1nqqmzngdosa911z9l2g8k8317/slide/9 |archivedate=2 September 2015}}</ref><ref name=\"Copa Am\u00e9rica 2016: Awards\" />\n* [[Argentine Football Association|Argentine Football Assn. Team of All Time]] (published 2015)<ref>{{cite web |title=La Selecci\u00f3n de Todos los Tiempos |trans-title=The Team of All Time |publisher=Argentine Football Association |language=Spanish |date=4 January 2016 |url=http://www.afa.com.ar/3023/la-seleccion-de-todos-los-tiempos |accessdate=8 January 2016 |website=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814210638/http://www.afa.com.ar/3023/la-seleccion-de-todos-los-tiempos |archive-date=14 August 2018 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* [[Laureus World Sports Award for Sportsman of the Year|Laureus World Sportsman of the Year]]: 2020<ref>{{cite news |title=Messi wins the Laureus award for 'Best Sportsman of the Year' |url=https://www.fcbarcelona.com/en/news/1613453/messi-wins-the-laureus-award-for-best-sportsman-of-the-year |accessdate=17 February 2020 |agency=FC Barcelona}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n{{Portal|Association football|Argentina}}\n* [[List of one-club men in association football]]\n* [[List of men's footballers with 50 or more international goals]]\n* [[List of footballers with 100 or more caps]]\n* [[Football records and statistics in Spain]]\n* [[UEFA club competition records and statistics]]\n* [[FIFA World Cup awards]]\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist-ua}}\n{{Reflist|group=note}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n'''Bibliography'''\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite book |title=Messi |last=Balagu\u00e9 |first=Guillem |date=2013 |publisher=Orion Books |isbn=978-1-4091-4659-9 |ref=harv |url-access=registration |url=https://archive.org/details/messibiography0000bala }}\n* {{cite book |title=Messi: The Inside Story of the Boy Who Became a Legend |last=Caioli |first=Luca |date=2012 |publisher=Corinthian Books |isbn=978-1-906850-40-1 |ref=ha